cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a method for image classification using convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The method is focused on semi-supervised and supervised learning, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses data augmentation, which is a common technique in natural language processing (cs.CL) and neural networks (cs.NE).
